item.description: Meet at Cutler Park at 9:30 AM... Parking area is right off Kendrick. We will cycle 15-20 miles on quiet roads into Needham-Dover. Those interested can go to Panera for coffee .if you email me, I am happy to exchange cell phone info. Meet at 9:30 at the Trail Stand, depart by 9:45 >>> So where's the CULTURE? at our rest stops, we will discuss ideas for Fall and Winter culture! ..I am posting to a couple of my other meetups.
item.name: Cutler Park - cycling country roads Mon Oct 10
